'''Docking Bay 68''' was a docking bay in [[Mos Tommro Spaceport]] on [[Cilpar]]. [[Lando Calrissian/Legends|Lando Calrissian]] docked the [[Lady Luck/Legends|''Lady Luck'']] there when he visited the [[Planet/Legends|world]] in [[19 ABY/Legends|19 ABY]].

